{"tid":1645014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事實就係有一班人無論點都會戴口罩落街，愈多人戴佢地就愈安全。","createTime":"2019-10-10T17:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T05:43:27.000Z","uid":36797,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd67002a7eeface212b408ff688c216fa6f9b04","tid":1645014,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"警告你地咪再叫人上街帶口罩, 手足女手足會比你地害死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644771</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到依個post好怕大家唔戴落去，我唔鐘意話前線既，或者示威者係年輕人，因為我覺得依個唔應該係年輕人既抗爭，而係香港人既抗爭。<br />\n但事實係街上有好多年輕人會日日戴口罩，前日將軍澳亦都有細路喺幾個人面前直接拐左上私家車，無人知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n出面係危險，但如果全街都肯戴，大家守望相助(好老土但真係) 提高警覺，佢地會少一分危險。<br />\n<br />\n差佬欺善怕惡，見到細路女人就恰，對住大叔師奶就龜縮，我地無人戴罩出街即係示弱，佢地就猖狂起黎。<br />\n<br />\n加油，香港人，反抗。"},{"pid":"e53e523a4a02d1a6b333ce3678f82a1fad62159b","tid":1645014,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ede777a4abb8d5d2c006f8611c31be48aa5a9699","tid":1645014,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f20da1e8728fe62cfd5eec09a96348cb9a6f123","tid":1645014,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:58:44.000Z","msg":"10月6日至10月7日 以下句子一直蔓延 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&quot;<strong>等美國通過法案啦 忍下手啦 唔差在呢幾日啦, 我地比律師朋友做野啦 休息啦..............&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果呢? 呢幾日發生咩事啊?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看更因為拒絕比暴徒進入住所被捕<br />\n暴徒街上亂咁拉 有無口罩都拉<br />\n黨鐵日日宵禁 屈示威者<br />\n浮屍又出現 未成年既都有</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n你班休息撚係咪又想<span style=\"color: red;\">等等等</span>?<br />\n等到<span style=\"color: red;\">新彊嶺建成全港200萬人一齊送入去集中營先行動好無?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再信咩野仲有幾多日通法案忍下手<br />\n咩野律師朋友做緊野忍下手<br />\n咩野民意逆轉外媒唔鐘意暴力忍下手<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場不是不合作運動, 呢場不是公民抗命咁簡單<br />\n呢場係一場革命, 係一場戰爭, 雙方都將所有賭本儘押<br />\n根本係無任何空間可以喘息 你估暴徒一方就算無活動, 又唔係晚晚開OT搜證拉人咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估林鄭開行會無傾過動用更多緊急法咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\">只要人,<strong>一齊趕絕休息撚 付諸行動 自己香港要自己救<br />\n<br />\n不要將抗爭外判 不要愧對義士 不要令自己後悔</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1ERLcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1ERLcz.jpg&h=1ea16afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59b8e4d52d635915651f4efa4cba6275658feab3","tid":1645014,"uid":115469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:59:55.000Z","msg":"推！要保護手足就麻煩你戴口罩出街啦<br />\n之後再鼓勵身邊嘅人一齊帶"},{"pid":"909254b5a9378e3378dd57dd6df2d6dd1b3dd8d0","tid":1645014,"uid":294068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img s