T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"想問下平日戴口罩對中共或者對警察構成乜野傷害？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"覺得戴罩冇用入嚟睇睇，絕對唔撚係左膠抗爭咁簡單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d49e2009ee39417691860874336952bab9fa66f","tid":1645014,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2820c696ae8fc978c16c5cb13d8ffd54ec78cd28","tid":1645014,"uid":36797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aacc30c736afd043c71ece411df1343c2147cb95","tid":1645014,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"想問下平日戴口罩對中共或者對警察構成乜野傷害？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"覺得戴罩冇用入嚟睇睇，絕對唔撚係左膠抗爭咁簡單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:19:37.000Z","msg":"你呢堆假設要全香港八成人肯做先有效<br />\n事實就係少人做嘅話反而變左明顯目標<br />\n而且唔係個個俾狗逗都冇風險<br />\n你仲停留喺形式主義嘅示威"},{"pid":"86ec1b40e282d4db287ca2d81cfeba4e6c80b5a7","tid":1645014,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"而家做既人數當係一成，依一成人係會一直做，你勸唔到佢唔做。<br />\n正如之前成日有人話前線送頭，明明應該退又唔退，但就係永遠會有人繼續做。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地唔可以降低依10%就應該諗下點樣提升佢。"},{"pid":"7615fe9386aaca637306d9afe39e5cdb17b4aa9f","tid":1645014,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4c526aece5f795f2c81c22c4b0efc74be01863","tid":1645014,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91f5c1e575366ddae463e78cdb4851b0b247af14",